{"abstract": "The company, having done polls through video games in 2012, plans to have its automated digital assistant survey people through their mobile phones.", "web_url": "https://www.nytimes.com/2014/09/30/upshot/microsoft-begins-a-push-into-the-polling-world.html", "snippet": "The company, having done polls through video games in 2012, plans to have its automated digital assistant survey people through their mobile phones.", "lead_paragraph": "People are slowly getting used to asking digital assistants like Apple\u2019s Siri simple questions, like \u201cWill it rain tomorrow?\u201d and \u201cWhere was Justin Bieber arrested?\u201d Soon, cellphones may be the ones doing the asking \u2014 surveying people on more serious matters like their choice for president and how the United States should confront the Islamic State.", "print_section": "A", "print_page": "3", "source": "The New York Times", "multimedia": [{"rank": 0, "subtype": "xlarge", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2014/09/30/upshot/30up-survey/30up-survey-articleLarge.jpg", "height": 600, "width": 600, "subType": "xlarge", "crop_name": "articleLarge", "legacy": {"xlarge": "images/2014/09/30/upshot/30up-survey/30up-survey-articleLarge.jpg", "xlargewidth": 600, "xlargeheight": 600}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "jumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2014/09/30/upshot/30up-survey/30up-survey-jumbo.jpg", "height": 1024, "width": 1024, "subType": "jumbo", "crop_name": "jumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "superJumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2014/09/30/upshot/30up-survey/30up-survey-superJumbo.jpg", "height": 2048, "width": 2048, "subType": "superJumbo", "crop_name": "superJumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "thumbnail", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2014/09/30/upshot/30up-survey/30up-survey-thumbStandard.jpg", "height": 75, "width": 75, "subType": "th